Tamiya.

68
00:04:58,256 --> 00:05:02,156
I'm Ryoko Tamiya.
It's a pleasure to meet you.

69
00:05:02,256 --> 00:05:04,056
[MIGI] It's her.
[SHINICHI] What?!

70
00:05:04,156 --> 00:05:08,456
And, as of today, Mr. Yamamoto
will be the new homeroom teacher
for Class 3‐3.

71
