After taking over the host,
[PE TEACHER] I don't wanna
see any crap out there.

83
00:05:47,223 --> 00:05:51,589
she has managed to
successfully maintain
their position in society.

84
00:05:51,689 --> 00:05:54,889
Plus, she functions as
a teacher of humans.

85
00:05:54,989 --> 00:05:57,123
She appears to be quite gifted.

86
00:05:57,223 --> 00:05:59,289
What are you praising her for?

87
00:05:59,389 --> 00:06:01,023
We have to do something.

88
00:06:01,123 --> 00:06:02,223
[MIGI] What do you mean?

89
00:06:02,323 --> 00:06:03,389
Well, what if we don't?

90
00:06:03,489 --> 00:06:04,989
She's gonna eat everybody!

91
00:06:05,089 --> 00:06:07,223
[MIGI] No, I highly doubt that.

92
00:06:07,323 --> 00:06:10,156
She wishes to blend in
with human society.

93
00:06:10,256 --> 00:06:11,889
I do not believe that
she would use anyone

94
00:06:11,989 --> 00:06:15,289
in her immediate social circle
as a food supply.

95
00:06:15,389 --> 00:06:18,223
Therefore,
I believe they should be safe.

96
00:06:18,323 --> 00:06:19,623
You don't know that.

97
00:06:19,723 --> 00:06:22,289
[MIGI] We should just
observe her for now.

98
00:06:32,856 --> 00:06:35,123
With everything that's
going on right now,

99
00:06:35,223 --> 00:06:37,389
how can Migi go to sleep?

100
00:06:37,489 --> 00:06:40,789
I mean, what if she
suddenly tries to...

101
00:06:40,889 --> 00:06:43,756
[RYOKO] All right, class.
I want you to use this formula

102
00:06:43,856 --> 00:06:46,656
to solve problems
six through twelve.

103
00:06:53,856 --> 00:06:56,189
[RYOKO] Mr. Izumi...
[SHINICHI] Oh, my God!

104
00:06:56,289 --> 00:06:58,156
Is there a problem?

105
00:06:58,256 --> 00:07:00,223
You don't appear
to have made any progress.

106
00:07:00,323 --> 00:07:03,123
Huh?! Uh... No, ma'am.

107
00:07:03,223 --> 00:07:06,023
Sorry.
(students laughing)

108
00:07:06,123 --> 00:07:09,023
(bell tolling)

109
00:07:09,123 --> 00:07:13,423
Mr. Izumi, would you
please visit me in the
counselor's office later?

110
00:07:15,089 --> 00:07:16,756
Thank you.

111
00:07:21,256 --> 00:07:23,356
Whoa... what'd you do?
[SHINICHI] Uh...

112
00:07:23,456 --> 00:07:25,156
Dude, how did you do that?

113
00:07:25,256 --> 00:07:28,523
Jesus, what do I have to do to
get myself called to the
teacher's office?!

114
00:07:28,623 --> 00:07:31,089
Hellooo? What's wrong with
what's sitting right here...

115
00:07:31,189 --> 00:07:32,989
